{"article_id":"Lz4SlwieJyiHTcck","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Sen. Joe Manchin , the West Virginia Democrat","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"who lent his name to bipartisan legislation","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that would have extended background checks for gun purchasers to gun shows and online sales ,","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"is n't letting go .","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"To Manchin , the bipartisan compromise","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"he co-sponsored with Sen. Pat Toomey , a Pennsylvania Republican of consistent conservative credentials ,","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"fell victim to a steady stream of misinformation","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"spread by some gun rights absolutists ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"including the National Rifle Association .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"The NRA disputes that characterization , of course .","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"But at a breakfast meeting Friday","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"hosted by Third Way , a Washington group","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"that pushes compromise solutions ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Manchin said","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"once Americans get a clearer view of the plan ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Congress could face renewed pressure","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"to pass a plan","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"that has overwhelming support in public opinion polls .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"`` When people start knowing","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that we have such a common-sense piece of legislation ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"[ the NRA 's tactics ,","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"which included claims","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"that the measure would have led to a national gun registry and gun confiscations ]","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"can backfire , ''","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Manchin said .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"`` Because , really , 80 to 90 percent of the people say ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"'That makes sense .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"' I 'm telling you , in the gun culture","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"I come from ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"I can go to Oklahoma","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"and I can go to anywhere in this country , and to the most fierce advocates of gun rights ,","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"and this will make sense","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"if they read it . ''","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Noting that his proposal is still technically `` on the floor ''","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"- meaning","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"while it 's been set aside ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid has the right under Senate rules","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"to call it back up -","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Manchin urged supporters to focus efforts on educating gun owners about the actual details of his plan .","depth":4},{"id":40,"text":"But that seems like wishful thinking at best .","depth":4},{"id":41,"text":"The Senate seems ready to move on to other agenda items ,","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"including an immigration overhaul plan ,","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"that might actually garner enough bipartisan support","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"to go somewhere .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"During the lead up to Wednesday 's Senate vote , one of the NRA 's most powerful threats was to hold accountable senators","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"who backed the measure .","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"And especially in conservative states , the NRA and its money can sway elections .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"That 's not likely to change .","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"Manchin said","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"the fear played on some senators","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"and acknowledged another problem for his side :","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"Two of the leaders","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"most identified with tougher gun laws","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"- President Obama and New York Mayor Michael Bloomberg -","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"make many on the gun rights side instantly suspicious .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"`` President Obama polls very bad in my state","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"and has not done well in my state , ''","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"said Manchin .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"`` But","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"if you want to blame somebody ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"blame me .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"This is not the president 's bill .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"I ca n't say it any plainer than that .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"... If you 're trying to put the president 's picture on it","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"because you think","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"you can get more no votes ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"that 's disingenuous .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"It 's not American . ''","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":137,"left":101,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":72,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":71,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":71,"left":0,"right":70,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":76,"right":99,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":76,"left":73,"right":75,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":73,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":6,"right":74,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":9,"right":98,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":98,"left":83,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":79,"right":82,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":79,"left":78,"right":13,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":78,"left":10,"right":77,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"par